dBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:39:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收皮啦 哈古龍</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nching係咪認錯人"},{"pid":"8fce236567032693c4c6251ab5daf9a060e71476","tid":27680,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:39:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n話左日日開"},{"pid":"3b6379e5d9080550af6ba4a205d4be3301fb864c","tid":27680,"uid":50969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:41:01.000Z","msg":"兩眼一黑 然後失控"},{"pid":"3ee05fe6c43392d121bfe72c59b17a5c6e7542f3","tid":27680,"uid":8572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:02:56.000Z","msg":"幫助別人改變命運，自己的命運也就同時得到潛移默化的改變。<br />\n<br />\n經常看到一些人戒色文章學習了不少，覺悟也看似提高了，但心魔來臨時就又成了擺設，極度痛苦地懊悔著。原因就在於覺悟還不夠全面、清晰和精煉。對此，我力荐的方法就是鼓勵吧友，解答疑惑。<br />\n<br />\n萬丈深淵中懊喪的你請不要再抱怨自己什麼都做到了卻還屢戒屢破，破戒，一定是有原因的，破戒，一定說明你還有做得不夠好的地方。<br />\n平庸者往往一面在對眼前機會的嫌棄中游手好閒，一面覺得自己是&quot;世界上最努力的人&quot;，而對這個&quot;不公平的世界&quot;產生消極、仇恨。而不凡之人時刻保持著一顆謙謹的心，永不停息地檢視並改進自己。<br />\n<br />\n屢戒屢破，嗯？那請每天毫不敷衍地解答10個、20個甚至更多吧友的疑惑、真心地鼓勵他們，看看自己還會不會瘋狂破戒。"},{"pid":"98aacab5c946ed3d947b20a37ea975c36b476031","tid":27680,"uid":7124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:07:25.000Z","msg":"我根本不比別人優秀⋯⋯"},{"pid":"490671ee6ca0cae73d0adea720dfdd81cf138024","tid":27680,"uid":42372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:30:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65125fb6a4169691d4cdc00dabd2fb0845ae866","tid":27680,"uid":12048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:32:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又係你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話左日日開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n愛一個人就是希望他過的更好<br />\n雖然難受但也必須酷酷的離別<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 共勉之"},{"pid":"8ecb25895d20f6041788c8d5e2240d7a097bcca2","tid":27680,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:34:28.000Z","msg":"我要再關心你 我有資格慰問你<br />\n我可以騷擾你 我就係咁撚厚面皮"},{"pid":"be009c6f65ac93605830bc99b10ac6fb3e8c2318","tid":27680,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:35:09.000Z","msg":"笠you"},{"pid":"ef254dc87a994e042c7bf7719bb4126dc9017dd6","tid":27680,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:02:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又係你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話左日日開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n愛一個人就是希望他過的更好<br />\n<br />\n雖然難受但也必須酷酷的離別<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 共勉之</blockquote><br />\n最緊要佢鐘意"},{"pid":"2f8c4de0a2377414d6a9b8a70938ae2ee3ad1f45","tid":27680,"uid":12048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:05:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又係你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話左日日開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n愛一個人就是希望他過的更好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然難受但也必須酷酷的離別<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 共勉之</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最緊要佢鐘意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n然後就祝褔佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n轉身走人"},{"pid":"208ab098cef9788a84ee609c91eff8ac2008dfe6","tid":27680,"uid":7124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:05:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我要再關心你 我有資格慰問你<br />\n我可以騷擾你 我就係咁撚厚面皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4083ca52a42b41887e37b4391b7415fb1f745d2","tid":27680,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:08:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我要再關心你 我有資格慰問你<br />\n<br />\n我可以騷擾你 我就係咁撚厚面皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"077c8b1c39f658fed2b20e9335db179562e840d4","tid":27680,"uid":12048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:09:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我要再關心你 我有資格慰問你<br />\n<br />\n我可以騷擾你 我就係咁撚厚面皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只會令人討厭你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14d30879b3adb0a3acea92178278fc658771e28","tid":27680,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:11:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我要再關心你 我有資格慰問你<br />\n<br />\n我可以騷擾你 我就係咁撚厚面皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只會令人討厭你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n纜炒好過 唔好再做埋d無謂施捨好似係到吊鹽水咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b84722e88cbd0ef3acd467cfc844ddc20e83a0","tid":27680,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:13:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我要再關心你 我有資格慰問你<br />\n<br />\n我可以騷擾你 我就係咁撚厚面皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只會令人討厭你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n纜炒好過 唔好再做埋d無謂施捨好似係到吊鹽水咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nChing好波"},{"pid":"6841de4a5076b744605c3c7b5e201e93c092fb09","tid":27680,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:15:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我要再關心你 我有資格慰問你<br />\n<br />\n我可以騷擾你 我就係咁撚厚面皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只會令人討厭你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n纜炒好過 唔好再做埋d無謂施捨好似係到吊鹽水咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nChing好波</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我唔想"},{"pid":"59da581f078edcbd2802530661970c5963f72299","tid":27680,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:18:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自由是天多遠多高 不怕 自豪地飛出去吧 <br />\n那矛盾一生聽過了 算吧 算吧 忘記吧 <br />\n<br />\n聽聽滿山春風 柔和地說話 終於我明白 <br />\n看看滿野花草 纏綿地躺下 <br />\n記憶中你很重我得放下 <br />\n漫步我天下 現在我更快樂嗎 <br />\n<br />\n難道我存在是為了你 纏住你永遠都飛不起 <br />\n懷念夠下決心摘去你 終於我拍翼能飛 自由地飛 <br />\n尋覓我回頭便沒有你 雲霧裡飛躍嬉戲 <br />\n明白我存在是為了我 逼不得已決定離開你 <br />\n畢竟不停有好天氣 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽聽故鄉的海 鯨魚在說話 形容我的家 <br />\n徘徊紅綠馬路 就讓我選擇 <br />\n要花盡力氣的愛太蒼白 <br />\n為何放不下 現在我更快樂嗎 <br />\n<br />\n難道我存在是為了你 纏住你永遠都飛不起 <br />\n懷念夠下決心摘去你 逼不得已決定離開你 <br />\n畢竟不能永久承受你 <br />\n<br />\n或者 也許 結果 不知道 <br />\n是否 究竟 最終 不知道 <br />\nDa di do Da di do Da di do <br />\nDa di do Da di do Da di do do di do <br />\n<br />\n難道我存在是為了你 纏住你永遠都飛不起 <br />\n懷念夠下決心摘去你 這刻我拍翼能飛 自由地飛一飛 <br />\n尋覓我回頭便沒有你 雲霧裡飛啊飛 <br />\n我明白到存在是為了我 <br />\n天空海闊決定離開你 再不提起 <br />\n飛出去 不相信明日無甜夢可期 不准放棄</span></span>"}]}